Question: Which of the following pairs will not form a balanced equation ?
Solution_text:
To check equality of expressions we will check if both of them give same result or not
First expression $23 - 18 = 5$
Second expression $9 * 10 = 90$
Since both expressions give different values, they do not form a balanced equation
